"discussions, please visit <a href=http://zzz.i2p/ target=_blank "
"rel=noreferrer class=sitelink>zzz's developer forums</a> or come and visit "
"the <a href=irc://127.0.0.1:6668/i2p-dev class=chatlink>developer "
"channel</a> on I2P's IRC network."
msgstr ""
"Si vous souhaitez signaler un bug, veuillez créer un ticket sur <a "
"href=https://github.com/I2PPlus/i2pplus/issues target=_blank rel=noreferrer "
"class=sitelink>github.com/I2PPlus/i2pplus/issues</a>. Pour les discussions "
"liées aux développeurs, veuillez visiter <a href=http://zzz.i2p/ "
"target=_blank rel=noreferrer class=sitelink>les forums des développeurs de "
"zzz</a> ou passer sur <a href=irc://127.0.0.1:6668/i2p-dev class=chatlink>le"
" canal de développement</a> du réseau IRC I2P."

msgid "Further assistance is available here:"
msgstr "Une assistance supplémentaire est proposée ici:"

msgid "I2P Support Forum"
msgstr "Forum d''assistance I2P"

msgid "I2P Developers' Forum"
msgstr "Forum des développeurs I2P"

msgid "I2P Wiki"
msgstr "Wiki I2P"

msgid ""
"The FAQ on <a href=http://i2p-projekt.i2p/en/faq target=_blank "
"rel=noreferrer>i2p-projekt.i2p</a> or <a href=https://geti2p.net/en/faq "
"target=_blank rel=noreferrer>geti2p.net</a>"
msgstr ""
"La FAQ sur <a href=http://i2p-projekt.i2p/en/faq target=_blank "
"rel=noreferrer>i2p-projekt.i2p</a> ou <a href=https://geti2p.net/en/faq "
